DomainData.MainInfoText: Meta inti żżur kwalunkwe sit web, jista’ jaħżen jew isib informazzjoni fuq il-brawżer tiegħek, l-aktar fil-forma ta’ cookies. Din l-informazzjoni tista’ tkun dwarek, dwar il-preferenzi tiegħek, it-tagħmir tiegħek jew tintuża biex tagħmel is-sit jaħdem kif inti tistenna li jkun. L-informazzjoni normalment ma tidentifikax lilek direttament, iżda tista’ tagħtik esperjenza tal-web aktar personalizzata. Inti tista’ tagħżel li ma tippermettix xi tipi ta’ cookies. Ikklikkja fuq l-intestaturi ta’ kategoriji differenti biex issir taf aktar u tibdel is-settings prestabbiliti tagħna. Madankollu, inti għandek tkun taf li meta timblokka xi tipi ta’ cookies, dan jista’ jimpatta l-esperjenza tiegħek fuq is-sit u s-servizzi li aħna nistgħu noffru.
DomainData.AlertNoticeText: Aħna nużaw il-cookies biex nippermettu s-sit tagħna jaħdem kif suppost, nippersonalizzaw il-kontenut u r-reklami, biex nipprovdu l-karatteristiċi tal-midja soċjali u biex nanalizzaw it-traffiku tagħna. Aħna nikkondividu wkoll l-informazzjoni dwar l-użu tiegħek tas-sit tagħna mal-imsieħba tagħna tal-midja soċjali, tar-reklamar u tal-analitika.

FirstPartyCookies.thirdPartyDescription: This cookie is set by the Google Analytics and determines new sessions and visits.  It expires after 30 minutes. The cookie is updated every time data is sent to Google Analytics. Any activity by a user within the 30 minute life span will count as a single visit, even if the user leaves and then returns to the site. A return after 30 minutes will count as a new visit, but a returning visitor.

Din il-cookie tiddetermina sessjonijiet u żjarat ġodda u tiskadi wara 30 minuta. Il-cookie tiġi aġġornata kull darba li tintbagħat id-data lil Google Analytics. Kwalunkwe attività minn utent fi ħdan it-tul tal-ħajja ta '30 minuta tgħodd bħala żjara waħda, anke jekk l-utent jitlaq u mbagħad jirritorna fis-sit. Ritorn wara 30 minuta se jgħodd bħala żjara ġdida, iżda viżitatur li jirritorna.

FirstPartyCookies.thirdPartyDescription: This cookie is set by the Google Analytics and is used to calculate new and returning visitor statistics. In this older versions this was used in combination with the __utmb cookie to identify new sessions/visits for returning visitors.  When used by Google Analytics this is always a Session cookie which is destroyed when the user closes their browser.
